        <description>Matching ID = MCN + FUA + PID + Order Product ID

*MCN:*Order.qtc_Master_Customer_Number__c
FUA: Order.qtc_Deliver_To_Site_Number__c 
PID: Product2.ProductCode
Order Product ID: Weâ€™ll use Order Product ID for now, and update to Fulfillment Order ID once Dev Complete.</description>
